Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:00.46,main,lily,0000,0000,0000,,Exhaustion Recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:05.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Lily always heals the people \Nof Hage Village with her sweet smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:09.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And it's said that it's the Hage \NHot Spring that heals her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:13.54,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But there are times when she's so \Nbusy with her duties at the church
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:15.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,that even a hot spring is not \Nenough to help her recover.
