Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:24.79,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Father introduced me to these, and they \Nworked instantly the day after I ate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:29.42,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Order now, and we'll throw in some \Ngarlic extract-infused moguro leaf juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.02,italics,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Order now!
