Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:33.05,sign_33829_368_Order_now_for_fr,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Order now for free shipping!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:33.05,sign_33829_369_Don_t_wait__Orde,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Don't wait! Order now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:35.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's on an infomercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:38.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister is as beautiful as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:41.87,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.98,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno are working so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:46.61,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the church is proud of you two.
